  "texts": [
    "Moreover, a base predictor was used for each neural network.",
    "To forecast the current student's course success, all predictors will be combined into an ensemble predictor using weights from several years.",
    "The predicted model's accuracy achieved was about 89.62%.",
    "A study by Yang et al (2022) is similar to the research by Kuo et al (2021), which suggested combining the DNN with K-means algorithms to predict student grades.",
    "Firstly, two public educational data sets (mathematics and Portuguese) were subjected to data mining and analysis techniques."
